*:

1. *Sam* se iznenadio kad je čuo novosti. (He was surprised when he heard the news.)

2. *Sam* ću otići do tržnog centra. (I will go to the mall by myself.)

3. On je *sam* sedeo u kući. (He was sitting at home alone.)

4. Ona je *sama* učinila to. (She did it all by herself.)

5. On je *sam* počeo da radi. (He started to work by himself.)

6. *Sama* je donela odluku. (She made the decision by herself.)

7. Oni su *sam*i završili posao. (They finished the job by themselves.)